<title>LET US HEAR YOU TELL IT</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw suohpih na gen tam, Lalpa ngaihdam zie?
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen;
 Kross' a A thihna ah Hukdam di'n na hung,
 Avela na genna chu kiza sawn hen;
 A vak nuom achn tuhin na leng em?
 Gitloh nin cheng apat na thieng em?
 Suna na nawpna zana na la ahim?
 A vela na genna chu kiza sawn hen.

[V2]
 Na genna chuh kizasawn hen,
 Genin, genin, gen sawn in;
 Thusim ngaihnawp um chuh genin,
 Hun panpih ina, lopi di'n,
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen.

[V3]
 2. Na sepgimna ah Hukdampa a um em?
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen;
 Isu'n zainem takin A hun enkawl em?
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen;
 Sepgim, natna a nang hun panpih thei,
 Amah bang guol dang muzo puon la;
 Nang dinga A thilbawl khawvel in heu hen,
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen.

[V4]
 3. Thu deihum chuh na lei in agen ngei em?
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen;
 Thildang cheng sanga lunggil kipak sak zaw,
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen;
 Khawvel mi lunggil natna'n a dim ui,
 A chawlhna hawl uh a thawn ahi;
 Thu leh la'n Isu chu amau hetsak in,
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen.

[V5]
 4. Na galdona haw a na zawhna haw chuh,
 A vela na genna chuh kizawn hen;
 Ziechun galdo tung mite panpih ina,
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen;
 Gitloh sepaihte tawh I kido ui,
 Hukdampa, Krista tawh vaihawm ding;
 Lalpa tatdawk te'n thagau mang mat guou in,
 A vela na genna chuh kiza sawn hen.</lyrics>
</song>